How it works

Introducing Learnt.ai - a revolutionary collection of AI-powered content generation tools and AI chatbots that are specifically designed to support the common writing tasks of educationalists and learning and development professionals. Imagine being able to generate learning objectives on any topic of your choice, create engaging icebreakers and activities, write assessment questions with ease, and so much more.
Powered by the cutting-edge GPT language generation model, Learnt.ai harnesses the power of AI to generate human-like text that will amaze you. All you have to do is provide a couple of prompts and let the system do the rest. With its vast knowledge of statistical patterns in the training data, Learnt.ai can generate responses that are tailored to your specific needs.

It's important to note that these tools are not intended to replace the years of experience and expertise needed to deliver great learning and assessment experiences. Instead, they are designed to act as an aid for professionals working in the education field. They are meant to save you time, provide inspiration, and get your creative juices flowing. So, whether you're a seasoned pro or just starting out, Learnt.ai is here to make your design and delivery process that much easier.

Try it out today and experience the future of education!
Step 1
Select a tool or sidekick.
Write lesson plans, set homework tasks, generate icebreakers, create assessment questions, and much more.
Step 2
Enter your prompt.
This tells the AI tool what you're looking for.

Don't over think it

Tools or Sidekicks

We're so excited to introduce you to the tools and sidekick.
First things first, let's talk about our tools. They're designed to be super targeted and trained to help you with specific tasks. Need to create a lesson plan? Our lesson plan tool has got your back. Want to write a multiple choice question? Our multiple choice tool is here to make your life easier.

Now let's talk about our sidekicks. You're the superhero here, and our AI sidekicks are your trusty assistants.

Think of them like a junior colleague, but one that never sleeps and is always ready to lend a hand. You can ask them for ideas, get them to do mini writing tasks, and even use them as a source of inspiration. Each sidekick has their own specialisms, so be sure to check out what they can do!
